data.description: Custom built 2-story home located in the community of San Miguel at Canyon Sprigs! 4-Bedrooms and 3.5- baths. All granite kitchen, hardwood, and tile flooring throughout. $100K additional outdoor covered paradise entertainment dwelling! Smoker/fire pit, gas BBQ, built-in stereo system, oversize HOT TUB with high top table/seating, all stonework, no wood, tile roofing! Stainless steel kitchen, double oven with GAS cooking! Wine chiller as well. Large media room and 2nd living area. Garage has added fully finished storage or play area for kids. Home is fully landscaped with mature trees and plenty of plants and flowers. Gated community with all the amenities!
